@page "/"

<PageTitle>GamerBio · Biometric Telemetry</PageTitle>

<div class="home">
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hud-eyebrow">Wearable · ESP32-S3 → Raspberry Pi 5</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
            Real-time <span class="accent">biometric</span><br />
            telemetry for gamers.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
            심박수 · 피부전도도 · 피부온도를 실시간으로 수집·융합해 
            플레이어의 <strong>긴장 상태</strong>를 분석하고 시청자와 공유합니다.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="btn-hud primary" href="dashboard">
                <span class="ecg-mini" aria-hidden="true">♥</span> 라이브 대시보드 열기
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pipe">
        <div class="hud-panel node">
            <div class="node-ix mono">01</div>
            <div class="node-name">Wearable</div>
            <p>ESP32-S3 · FreeRTOS<br />MAX30102 · GSR · DS18B20</p>
            <div class="node-tag mono v-heart">SENSE</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-arrow mono">→</div>
        <div class="hud-panel node">
            <div class="node-ix mono">02</div>
            <div class="node-name">RPi5 Server</div>
            <p>ASP.NET 10 · SignalR<br />PostgreSQL 17</p>
            <div class="node-tag mono v-gsr">FUSE</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-arrow mono">→</div>
        <div class="hud-panel node">
            <div class="node-ix mono">03</div>
            <div class="node-name">Dashboard</div>
            <p>Blazor Server<br />Discord 알림 · MJPEG</p>
            <div class="node-tag mono v-temp">SHARE</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="states">
        <div class="hud-eyebrow">Tension classification</div>
        <div class="state-row">
            <span class="chip s-relaxed">😏 Relaxed</span>
            <span class="chip s-focused">🥺 Focused</span>
            <span class="chip s-stressed">🥵 Stressed</span>
            <span class="chip s-calib">⏳ Calibrating</span>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
